{
  "id": "adv_main_02_01_02",
  "title": "東京編1章2話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、怜ちゃん、遙子ちゃん\nお待たせ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Rei-chan! Haruko-chan!\nSorry we’re late!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.231578912233052,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 0.36666666666666664
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、みんな\nこっちはもう準備出来てるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ everyone.\nEverything’s ready to go on our end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.133333285649618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、遙子さん\nみんなの分の飲み物まで用意してくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ Haruko-san.\nThat was nice of you to get drinks for everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.733333285649616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "いいのいいの\nむしろ、やらない方が落ち着かないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t mention it.\nActually‚ I’d feel less relaxed otherwise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.69999995231628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんは……早いね\nもうウォーミングアップ始めてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ Rei-chan… You sure are here early.\nYou’ve already started warming up‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.666666618982937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私も、体動かしていないと落ち着かないから\nそれより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also have a hard time relaxing if I’m not moving my body.\nAnyway…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.56666661898294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "その人、新しいマネージャーさんですよね？\nはじめまして、一ノ瀬怜です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the new manager‚ aren’t you?\nNice to meet you. I’m Rei Ichinose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5305388976366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子でーす\nみんなと同世代、ぴちぴちのじゅうなな歳――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I’m Haruko Saeki!\nI’m just like my fellow teens here—a sweet 17 years old!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.46387223096998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "す、すごい……感激です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wow… So epic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.73053889763665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrhrk-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 48.49720556430331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "溢れる母性でファンを癒やしまくる\n最年長のお姉さん系アイドル遙子さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With her motherly aura‚ she nurtures all her fans.\nThe eldest‚ big sister type idol—Haruko-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6972055643033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_chrrei-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg4",
      "startTime": 55.5284072448046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "ストイックでキレのあるダンスがカッコいい\nパフォーマーアイドル怜ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stoic and cool‚ the sharp-dancing\nperformance idol—Rei-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 62.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "お二人に会えるなんて……\nこの仕事、就いてよかった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t believe I get to meet you both…\nI’m so glad I chose this career!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さ、最年長……\nあの、えっと……ぴ、ぴちぴちのじゅうなな歳……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "E-eldest?\nUm‚ but I’m a s-sweet 17 years old…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "一度殺されたボケは……\n二度は通じない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once a joke is dead‚\nit’ll never be funny again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それより、早くレッスン始めない？\nせっかく揃ったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind that. Can we just start our lesson already?\nWe’re all here‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな\nでも、まずはその前に朝礼をさせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.\nBut before you do‚ let me give some announcements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 93
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……新しい仕事の連絡事項は以上だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that concludes all the new work announcements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュール、どんどん埋まっていくね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ our schedule’s filling up‚ huh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "早めにこっちに拠点を移しといて\n正解だったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moving here early\nwas definitely the right move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それぞれ、通学には不便を強いて悪いと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though I feel bad that it’s inconveniencing your schooling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私は気にしていません\nこっちの方が、より質の高いレッスン受けられますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind at all.\nLiving here‚ I can have much higher quality dance lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私もです。新しい寮での生活も\n慣れたら楽しいし……ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree. Life at our new dorm\nwill be fun once we’ve settled in… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも、グッズの入手しやすさも\n都内の方が、有利……だから、オッケー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lives‚ buying merch‚\neverything’s easier in Tokyo. So I’m cool with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると頑張って移転した甲斐があったよ\nでも今は、やはりグランプリ優勝の効果が大きい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hearing that makes me glad I did the work to get this transfer.\nBut your Grand Prix victory has had the most effect.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "気を抜くと、あっという間に他のグループに\n追い越されてしまいますよね。気を引き締めないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we let our guard down‚ it's easy for other groups to surpass us.\nWe need to stay focused and tighten our efforts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね……それに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s for sure. And besides‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんが戻ってきた時に\n輝いている私達を見て欲しいものね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "when Saegusa-san comes back‚\nI want him to see us really shine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "あの……三枝さんっていうのは\n面接の時にも言っていた、先代の社長さんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ but… this Saegusa-san‚\nhe’s the former president you mentioned at the interview‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 164.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_01_02-koh006.m4a",
